Package org.rd.switchboard.nexus.exporters.rda.json

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    Main class for Nexus RDA records exported Parameters: $1 : Neor4j main folder (neo4j) $2 : Output folder (rda/json) $3 : Export level (3) $4 : Maximum nodes per file (100) $5 : Maximum new siblings per node (10) Installation: To compile project, please execute: $ mvn package To run, please copy program jar file and whole jars directory from target into main project folder and run $ java -jar .jar
    Exporter
    Export RDA records from Nexus instance in JSON formats The maximum of Exporter.maxNodes nodes will be exported with Exporter.maxLevel level siblings.
